    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hey 👋, I'm Sascha and I develop Reforged Tower Defense in my spare time - simply because I love tower defense games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1044110/extras/b3983fff3413a3b4c2d748b0e522577e.webp?t=1746560639\" width=752 height=43 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1044110/extras/150ce099d45ed433e3c8e7fda3b79a89.poster.avif?t=1746560639\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1044110/extras/150ce099d45ed433e3c8e7fda3b79a89.webm?t=1746560639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1044110/extras/150ce099d45ed433e3c8e7fda3b79a89.mp4?t=1746560639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I wanted to build a game that captures the charm of classic TDs - but with a twist: loot, level system, skill trees and even co-op. Whether you just want to set towers until the enemy waves crash, or you want to perfect builds and strategies, you'll find your thing here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1044110/extras/42d5053538b9f9355d3285bc8a856b63.webp?t=1746560639\" width=751 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1044110/extras/5862d53a76cc43e17c913012d56d70f1.poster.avif?t=1746560639\" width=800 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1044110/extras/5862d53a76cc43e17c913012d56d70f1.webm?t=1746560639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1044110/extras/5862d53a76cc43e17c913012d56d70f1.mp4?t=1746560639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>There is no battle pass, no energy limit, no timer - just towers, opponents and your plan. Whether solo in classic or rogue-like mode or together in co-op - you decide how you want to play. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1044110/extras/202300e6bb300f322b85c3fd96c36ebb.webp?t=1746560639\" width=751 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1044110/extras/829505b1a1bdf5be80d285746167a0da.poster.avif?t=1746560639\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1044110/extras/829505b1a1bdf5be80d285746167a0da.webm?t=1746560639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1044110/extras/829505b1a1bdf5be80d285746167a0da.mp4?t=1746560639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have ideas for new towers, items or crazy game modes? Just write to me! I'm passionate about developing Reforged Tower Defense and welcome any input - be it bug reports, feedback or a wild wish list. If you want to see something cool in the game, let me know. Maybe it'll be in the next update. 💬</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks for joining us - and have fun defending!🛡💥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1044110/extras/836ee90b5d388c7b41f63fe4aff9e994.avif?t=1746560639\" width=674 height=103 /></span></p>",
